BERGENVOLUNTEERS
Invites You to:
Neighbors Helping Neighbors
Together, we will assemble essential care items
for our neighbors in need.
SNACKS | DRINKS | GIVING BACK
Sunday, December 7th
10:00 AM - 1:00 PM
Register here or scan below. Registration fee applies.*
14 V
All ages are welcome. Drop in any time to help!
Community service hours available upon request.
50 Eisenhower Drive, Paramus, NJ
For questions, contact hbaris@bergenvolunteers.org
*This fundraiser helps Bergen Volunteers to continue to support vulnerable populations in our community.
